==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Smokeless powder
<hw>Smoke"less pow"der</hw>. <def>A high-explosive gunpowder whose
explosion produces little, if any, smoke. It is usually based on
guncotton (nitrocellulose).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Smoke out</ent>⟦br⟧
